'''Nikol Švantnerová''' (born 21 October 1992) is a [[Czechs|Czech]] model and [[beauty pageant]] titleholder who was crowned [[Czech Miss|Česká Miss 2015]] and represented the [[Czech Republic]] at [[Miss Universe 2015]].

==Personal life==
Švantnerová was born in [[Šumperk]], but has lived in [[České Budějovice]] most of her life. She is currently a student and is completing her degree. In her spare time, she loves watching sports, especially football, with her family and friends. She is also fascinated with foreign languages and would like to learn French and Spanish someday.

===Česká Miss 2015===
Švantnerová was crowned Česká Miss 2015 and represented Šumperk at the pageant on 28 March 2015. The pageant aired live on FTV Prima.{{citation needed|date=March 2016}}

===Miss Universe 2015===
Švantnerová competed at the [[Miss Universe 2015]] pageant but did not place.

